~ start
King: Fools. You think this was chaos?
King: Every raid, every fire, every order was part of my design.
King: Fear is the fastest way to unite a kingdom.
Soldier: Your majesty... then the town attack was your command?
Soldier: We watched the messenger fight with magic for his people.
Soldier: If he is only a common messenger, why does he wield powers you never could?
King: Silence.
Soldier: The old records were true...
Soldier: He is blood of the rightful line, descendant of the king before the usurpation.
Soldier: Men, lower your weapons.
Soldier: Long live the true king!
Player: Bind him. He will answer for every village burned in his ambition.
Player: From this moment, mobilize the army immediately.
Player: We march to defend every town under this crown.
=> END
